---
const cards = [
  {
    title: "U.S. Based CFO Experts",
    desc: "Finkeepers bring in the deep knowledge of the U.S. markets their tax laws and regulations, and compliance and shifts. Hence, having a temporary CFO for your firm from Finkeepers will be a helpful hand and will easily ease into the routine of the firm. ",
  },
  {
    title: "Curated Strategies",
    desc: "Leveraging the expertise, the temporary CFO services of Finkeepers will be curated according to the needs of the firm, rather than applying generic and basic strategies. We understand that when it comes to making financial decisions, one size fits all is never an option.",
  },
  {
    title: "Actionable Solutions",
    desc: "The solutions provided by Finkeepers will not be fictional. Those will all be in regulation with market shifts, suggested after doing competitor analysis, and will deliver results instead of incurring losses, which small businesses cannot afford. ",
  },
  {
    title: "Support During Crisis",
    desc: "We do not abandon our own during times of need. Finkeepers will support small businesses of the U.S. during the time of crisis and help resurface them and make correct financial decisions. ",
  },
  {
    title: "Proven Track Record",
    desc: "Finkeepers have been helping small businesses in the U.S. survive the market and make profits with the help of temporary CFO services. WE streamline finances and establish systems that run long after the subscription period is over.",
  },
  
];
---

<div
  class="main-container w-full pt-[80px] pr-[20px] pb-[80px] pl-[20px] lg:pr-[120px] lg:pl-[120px] flex flex-col gap-[32px] justify-start items-start bg-[#106253] relative mx-auto"
>
  <!-- Heading -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1200px] flex justify-start items-center">
    <span
      class="font-['Inter'] text-[24px] sm:text-[28px] md:text-[32px] lg:text-[36px] font-bold leading-[1.2] text-white"
    >
     Why Choose Finkeepers as your Temporary CFOs?

    </span>
  </div>
 <div class="w-full max-w-[1200px]">
  <p class="text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#ffffff] text-left">
        Finkeepers understands the situations of the firms with no CFO, which is why we step in as an interim CFO until you can hire one permanently or have the capacity to promote one in-house.
      </p>
  </div>
  <!-- Cards Container -->
  <div class="w-full max-w-[1200px] flex flex-col gap-[25px]">
    <!-- Row 1 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-[25px]">
      {
        cards.slice(0, 3).map((card, index) => (
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-[18px] bg-[#0F5448] rounded-[16px] border border-[#0F5448] shadow-[0px 3px 10px 1px #0000001C] p-[20px] flex-1 
                      transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:z-10 relative"
          >
             <!-- Number in top-left corner -->
            <div class="absolute -top-[20px] -left-[20px] flex w-[40px] h-[40px] justify-center items-center bg-white rounded-full border-2 border-[#106253]"
            style="left: 15px">
              <span class="text-[#106253] font-bold text-[18px]">
                {String(index + 1).padStart(2)}
              </span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white font-semibold text-[20px] sm:text-[22px] leading-[28px] mt-4">
              {card.title}
            </span>
            <span class="text-white text-[16px] leading-[22px] font-['Inter']" style="letter-spacing: 0.3px;">
              {card.desc}
            </span>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>

    <!-- Row 2 -->
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-[25px]" style="margin-top: 10px;">
      {
        cards.slice(3).map((card, index) => (
          <div
            class="flex flex-col gap-[18px] bg-[#0F5448] rounded-[16px] border border-[#0F5448] shadow-[0px 3px 10px 1px #0000001C] p-[20px] flex-1 
                      transform transition-transform duration-300 ease-in-out hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:z-10 relative"
          >
            <!-- Number in top-left corner -->
            <div class="absolute -top-[20px] -left-[20px] flex w-[40px] h-[40px] justify-center items-center bg-white rounded-full border-2 border-[#106253]"
            style="left: 15px">
              <span class="text-[#106253] font-bold text-[18px]">
                {String(index + 4).padStart(2)}
              </span>
            </div>
            <span class="text-white font-semibold text-[20px] sm:text-[22px] leading-[28px] mt-4">
              {card.title}
            </span>
            <span class="text-white text-[16px] leading-[22px] font-['Inter']" style="letter-spacing: 0.3px;">
              {card.desc}
            </span>
          </div>
        ))
      }
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
